text: Juhani Ruotsalainen (1 April 1948–2015) was a Finnish ski jumper. He competed in the normal hill and large hill events at the 1968 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1948 births Category:2015 deaths Category:Finnish male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of Finland Category:Ski jumpers at the 1968 Winter Olympics Category:People from Iisalmi
